# Commit message template (Conventional Commits style)
# Example: feat(api): add /remember endpoint

<type>(<scope>): <short summary>

<body — optional, use to explain motivation and technical details>

Footer: Fixes #<issue-number> | Co-authored-by: Name <email>

# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci, revert
